examples.en: He has a humongous appetite and snores a lot.
We had a humongous row just because she left.
The restaurant was humongous and rammed to the gills.
She was seen hatched from a humongous blue egg that appeared with a train.
A large tall white dog, he has a good-natured personality but a humongous appetite.
If there was this vast and humongous conspiracy, its members had to number in the hundreds.
She lives in a humongous house on the hill. *
